OL,3,CIran strikes Kuwait oil refinery and
OL,4,Cclaims it shot down US fighter jet
OL,6,FIran has hit targets across the Middle
OL,7,FEast, including a refinery in Kuwait,
OL,8,Fwhile American and Israeli airstrikes
OL,9,Fhit the Islamic Republic as the war
OL,10,Fneared the end of its fifth week.
OL,12,FIranian state media also released
OL,13,Fphotos of what it claimed is the
OL,14,Fwreckage of a US Air Force fighter jet
OL,15,Fdowned by the Islamic Revolutionary
OL,16,FGuard Corps. The White House has yet
OL,17,Fto comment on the jet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
