OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775369052
OL,3,CIran strikes Kuwait oil refinery and
OL,4,Cclaims it shot down US fighter jet
OL,6,FIran's attacks on Gulf energy
OL,7,Finfrastructure and its tight grip on
OL,8,Fthe Strait of Hormuz, through which a
OL,9,Ffifth of the world's oil and natural
OL,10,Fgas transits in peacetime, have
OL,11,Fcontinued to disrupt stock markets and
OL,12,Fsend oil prices skyrocketing, and
OL,13,Fthreatened to raise the cost of many
OL,14,Fbasic goods, including food.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
