PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775369052
OL,3,CIran strikes Kuwait oil refinery and
OL,4,Cclaims it shot down US fighter jet
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,7,Fcondemned the drone attack on Kuwait
OL,8,Fin a call with the the Crown Prince of
OL,9,FKuwait, Sheikh Sabah Al-Khaled Al-
OL,10,FHamad Al-Mubarak Al-Sabah on Friday
OL,11,Fmorning.
OL,13,F"He reiterated that the UK stands with
OL,14,FKuwait and all our allies in the Gulf.
OL,15,FThey discussed the deployment of the
OL,16,FUK's Rapid Sentry air defence system
OL,17,Fto Kuwait, which will protect Kuwaiti
OL,18,Fand British personnel and interests in
OL,19,Fthe region, while avoiding escalation
OL,20,Finto wider conflict," a Downing Street
OL,21,Fspokesperson said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
