OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775369052
OL,3,CIran strikes Kuwait oil refinery and
OL,4,Cclaims it shot down US fighter jet
OL,6,F"Regarding ongoing disruption to
OL,7,Fglobal shipping through the Strait of
OL,8,FHormuz, the Prime Minister and Crown
OL,9,FPrince welcomed the meeting convened
OL,10,Fby the Foreign Secretary yesterday on
OL,11,Fa viable plan to reopen the Strait.
OL,13,F"They agreed to continue to work
OL,14,Ftogether on this and stay in close
OL,15,Fcontact over the coming weeks."
OL,17,FFrench ship passes through Strait of
OL,18,FHormuz
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@_O]
