PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775369052
OL,3,CIran strikes Kuwait oil refinery and
OL,4,Cclaims it shot down US fighter jet
OL,6,FMeanwhile a French-owned container
OL,7,Fship manage to cross the Strait of
OL,8,FHormuz late on Thursday, according to
OL,9,Fmarine traffic data, in what is
OL,10,Fbelieved to be the first Western-
OL,11,Fflagged vessel to pass through the
OL,12,Fchannel since the start of the current
OL,13,Fconflict.
OL,15,FA trickle of boats have crossed
OL,16,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz since
OL,17,FIran launched retaliatory strikes
OL,18,Ffollowing US-Israeli attacks on
OL,19,FTehran, and Iran has largely blocked
OL,20,Foff the crucial waterway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
