PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775369052
OL,3,CIran strikes Kuwait oil refinery and
OL,4,Cclaims it shot down US fighter jet
OL,6,FOn Thursday Foreign Secretary Yvette
OL,7,FCooper condemned "Iranian
OL,8,Frecklessness" for "hitting global
OL,9,Feconomic security" in talks with a
OL,10,Fcoalition of countries aimed at
OL,11,Freopening the vital Strait of Hormuz
OL,12,Fshipping lane for oil.
OL,14,FBritain is seeking to lead a
OL,15,Fdiplomatic initiative, including
OL,16,Fcountries such as France, Germany and
OL,17,Fsome Gulf nations, to restore access
OL,18,Fto the maritime route being throttled
OL,19,Fby Iran in retaliation for the US-
OL,20,FIsraeli campaign against it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
